{
  "texts": [
    "Step 2: Pre-experimental preparation.",
    "This stage focuses on conducting a basic information survey of the participants and preparing the necessary tools.",
    "Firstly, prior to the start of the experiment, a survey of the participants' basic information is conducted, along with an assessment of their familiarity with ChatGPT.",
    "Subsequently, the experimental tools are prepared by distributing a standardized Python installation package (version 3.9.5) and configuring the controlled variable of a unified version of the Matplotlib (version 3.7.0).",
    "This ensures the elimination of interference factors caused by differences in tool versions."
  ]
}